Subject: r8169: fix RTL8117 Wake-on-Lan in DASH mode
To: stable@vger.kernel.org
Cc: "RenÈ Rebe" <rene@exactco.de>, "Heiner Kallweit" <hkallweit1@gmail.com>, "Jakub Kicinski" <kuba@kernel.org>, "Sasha Levin" <sashal@kernel.org>
